cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper deals with computer vision and robotics, specifically in the area of automatic parking. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of surround-view images and fisheye cameras suggests that the paper could also be relevant to cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper's focus on detecting parking slots and road structures suggests that it could also be relevant to cs.RO (Robotics).
